==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oneness
<hw>One"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of being one; singleness
in number; individuality; unity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Our God is one, or rather very <qex>oneness</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Hooker.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Onerary</ent>⟦br⟧
